{
  "stem": "5471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We'll have there-- in the creche, too, for the kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but even-- I looked after two boys for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if they didn't feel well, they would say, oh, I'm not going to the work today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have pain in my toe or a pain in my tummy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or-- and I would say, listen, do me a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't try that in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here, you can do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But even there, try to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they said, oh, don't worry about us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We will be right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, none of them came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17, 18.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] You could say little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had in a-- very, very good hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Jewish hospital what was in Amsterdam, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the equipment was brought over to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had a marvelous hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was in a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a creche for kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had schooling, I think, till they were about 14.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sometimes, they went for a walk, those kids, and were singing along the road.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our [LAUGHS] little one always wanted to go with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were kiddies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she wanted to go with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had in a-- a laundry, big laundry, and the kitchen, and the hairdresser, and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like a little town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything what you find in a town, you had there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at certain times, we even got in a, a [NON-ENGLISH] and a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] was the Lager [NON-ENGLISH], a kind of movers, a kind of supermarket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had [NON-ENGLISH], the Lager canteen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they could get a cup of coffee with a biscuit at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
